CONTROL UNDEAD

Usage       : cast 'control undead' <victim>
Accumulative: No
Duration    : (432/Intelligence points of person) hours
Save	    : vs. paralysation

When cast on a creature of the undead race, it forces it to save verses
paralysation or become the antipaladin's loyal follower.  If the undead
creature saves, the creature will immediately attack.  Duration is similar
to charm monster.

See Also: CHARM MONSTER
Related Topics: SPELL INFO
